### Demonstrating Account Abstraction
### Create different account types and issue cards backed by each

### Create Internal Ledger Account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ownerId": "user-456",
  "accountType": "INTERNAL_LEDGER",
  "currency": "USD",
  "initialBalance": 500.00
}

###

